      {
        "name": "places/ChIJqXLkyCIttokRL7aDFgsmrWQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOR1FYaHFjM2czVlV0VFlYWm1aVUZhUkRod1UxRRAB",
        "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago",
        "rating": 5,
        "text": {
          "text": "I had an excellent experience working with New Funding Resources, especially Anastasia and Melissa, throughout my renovation loan process. As a first-time fix-and-flip investor, I had many questions and uncertainties, but they were there for me every step of the way.\n\nThey were incredibly responsive, transparent, and patient. Anastasia ensured the process moved smoothly and fairly, and Melissa was extremely organized and helpful during underwriting and documentation. I never felt lost or left on my own — they truly walked me through the entire process.\n\nWhat stood out most was how much they care about their clients’ success. They stand by their word, communicate clearly, and treat you like a real partner.\n\nIf you're looking for a trustworthy, knowledgeable, and professional lender, I highly recommend New Funding Resources.\n\nThank you again for everything!",
          "languageCode": "en"
        },
        "originalText": {
          "text": "I had an excellent experience working with New Funding Resources, especially Anastasia and Melissa, throughout my renovation loan process. As a first-time fix-and-flip investor, I had many questions and uncertainties, but they were there for me every step of the way.\n\nThey were incredibly responsive, transparent, and patient. Anastasia ensured the process moved smoothly and fairly, and Melissa was extremely organized and helpful during underwriting and documentation. I never felt lost or left on my own — they truly walked me through the entire process.\n\nWhat stood out most was how much they care about their clients’ success. They stand by their word, communicate clearly, and treat you like a real partner.\n\nIf you're looking for a trustworthy, knowledgeable, and professional lender, I highly recommend New Funding Resources.\n\nThank you again for everything!",
          "languageCode": "en"
        },
