      {
        "name": "places/ChIJqXLkyCIttokRL7aDFgsmrWQ/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNUa2JpQ1ZBEAE",
        "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago",
        "rating": 5,
        "text": {
          "text": "New Funding Resources has been a pleasure to work with throughout my loan application process.\nAfter speaking and qualifying with several other remote lenders I found New Funding Resources.\nI immediately noticed the difference from the other lenders. They were immediately responsive, efficient, and knowledgeable about the local real estate market. The entire application process was handled proficiently in house, by experienced senior staff, Melissa, and the owner, Kyle, unlike the other lenders with multiple entities and inexperienced staff. I immediately felt more comfortable with their straightforward and honest approach. They were flexible with their requirements, recognizing my unique conditions. The result was a very competitive cost with quick approval and no last minute surprises or problems. They have also developed an excellent follow-up support system and knowledge base to advise and support their investors. They want you to succeed. This lender checks all the boxes. Thank you, Melissa and Kyle, for the exceptional service.",
          "languageCode": "en"
        },
        "originalText": {
          "text": "New Funding Resources has been a pleasure to work with throughout my loan application process.\nAfter speaking and qualifying with several other remote lenders I found New Funding Resources.\nI immediately noticed the difference from the other lenders. They were immediately responsive, efficient, and knowledgeable about the local real estate market. The entire application process was handled proficiently in house, by experienced senior staff, Melissa, and the owner, Kyle, unlike the other lenders with multiple entities and inexperienced staff. I immediately felt more comfortable with their straightforward and honest approach. They were flexible with their requirements, recognizing my unique conditions. The result was a very competitive cost with quick approval and no last minute surprises or problems. They have also developed an excellent follow-up support system and knowledge base to advise and support their investors. They want you to succeed. This lender checks all the boxes. Thank you, Melissa and Kyle, for the exceptional service.",
          "languageCode": "en"
        },
        "authorAttribution": {
          "displayName": "Edward T.",
          "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102640387656247249790/reviews",
          "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJEqgTcvYvCLtqx6V21LEkwZ7icC-KVsSmVhjkHmWLHlNHULA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"
        },
        "publishTime": "2024-05-15T20:01:13.779585Z",
        "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/review/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNUa2JpQ1ZBEAE&d=17924085&t=1",
        "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNUa2JpQ1ZBEAE!2m1!1s0x89b62d22c8e472a9:0x64ad260b1683b62f"
      },
      {
        "name": "places/ChIJqXLkyCIttokRL7aDFgsmrWQ/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURqajlTUG5BRRAB",
        "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago",
        "rating": 5,
        "text": {
          "text": "I am so glad I found New Funding Resources. I wanted to sell an inherited property, but it needed a lot of work to list it. I was going into personal funds initially and putting stuff on my credit cards until I realized I just could not keep funding the project personally. I reached out to New Funding Resources to inquire about Hard Money for the renovations and thank God they were able to help. They gave me the cash I needed to get the repairs and renovations done that I needed. The turnaround time from application to receipt of funds was relatively quick. I cannot adequately express how grateful I am for their help. I had the pleasure of working with Anastasia and Melissa throughout and they both were just a joy to work with throughout. The contractors discovered a major problem with the downspouts and water going down to the foundation of my house and they needed to redo the entire drainage system. It was a major unexpected expense, but thanks to New Funding Resources I was able to get the job done. I have remained in contact with  New Funding Resources during the renovations and received some guidance on how to receive additional help should I need to do so to get the job done.\n\nI want to build on another lot I own in the near future, and I will probably use them to fund the construction there as well.  They were just there every step of the way on my current project, and they made the process easy. If you are thinking to fix and flip or to do construction, I suggest you give New Funding Resources a call and ask for Anastasia or Melissa. You will not regret the call. This has truly been the best experience for me and I am extremely grateful to them. Thanks so much to New Funding Resources!!",
          "languageCode": "en"
        },
        "originalText": {
